{
  "chapter": "020",
  "title": "建元以来侯者年表",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "太史公曰。"
    },
    "1.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>断绝<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">和亲</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻打</span>汉朝险要的关塞；<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">闽越</span>擅自<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">征伐</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东瓯</span>请求<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">归降</span>。"
    },
    "1.2": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "两支<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">夷</span>族交相来犯，正值<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝兴盛之时，由此可知此时<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">功臣</span>受封的规模可与祖宗时代相比。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "征伐夷狄应时而起。"
    },
    "2.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "为什么这样说呢？自从<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：诗\">诗经（诗）</span>经、<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：书\">尚书（书）</span>经称颂<span class=\"mythical\" title=\"神话\">三代</span>\"痛击<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">戎狄</span>，征伐<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">荆荼</span>\"，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桓</span>公越过<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>国<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">讨伐</span><span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">山戎</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武灵王</span>凭借区区<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国一国就降服了<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">单于</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">缪</span>公重用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">百里</span>奚而称霸<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">西戎</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>之君凭借<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>之位就役使百<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">越</span>。"
    },
    "2.2": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "何况<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">中国</span>如今一统，贤明的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>居上，兼有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文</span>王、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武</span>王之德，席卷四海之内，安抚亿万之众，岂能安然无事而不对接壤的边境施行<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">征</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">讨伐</span>呢！"
    },
    "2.3": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "从此以后，朝廷便出兵北<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">讨伐</span>强悍的<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">胡</span>人，南<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛灭</span>劲勇的<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">越</span>族，将卒们便依次得到封爵。"
    }
  }
}